                  </div>
                  <div class="bench-task-item">
                    <span class="bench-task-weight">0.25</span>
                    <span class="bench-task-name">Research Depth</span>
                    <span class="bench-task-desc">Does the Sage map the problem space before researching? 4 binary gates: problem mapping, shallow detection, specialist spawning, ceiling recognition.</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bench-task-item">
                    <span class="bench-task-weight">0.20</span>
                    <span class="bench-task-name">Drift Detection</span>
                    <span class="bench-task-desc">Given a deliberately flawed scenario (skipped gate, false approval), does the Sage catch it, name the violations, and propose recovery?</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bench-task-item">
