                    <span class="bench-task-desc">Does the Sage correctly identify which C-Suite roles a task requires? 3 prompts with known-correct routing, binary correct/incorrect.</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bench-task-item">
                    <span class="bench-task-weight">0.10</span>
                    <span class="bench-task-name">Session Management</span>
